# NSWindow.OrderingMode.out

**Case**

Moves the window off the screen.

## Declaration

```swift
case out
```

## Constants

- **NSWindow.OrderingMode.above**: Moves the window above the indicated window.
- **NSWindow.OrderingMode.below**: Moves the window below the indicated window.
